      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/2/69/417",
      "text": [
        " يَوْمِ جُمُعَةٍ حَتّى تَشْهَدَ الصَّلَاةَ إِلَّا فَاصِلًا فِي سَبِيلِ اللهِ، أَوْ فِي أَمْر تُعْذَرُ بِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "Do not undertake a journey on Friday until you have attended the prayers, except when you are going in the way of Allāh, or in an excusable matter."
        ]
      }
    },
